        <item>
          <title>Asus GPU Tweak III Gets Power Detector+ Warning for Critical Power Cable Issue</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Asus has released a new version of its GPU software suite with the Power Detector+ warning function, which warns users if any of the pins on their graphics card's power connector have too many amps flowing through them, potentially leading to a melted power cable disaster.]]></description>
